&nbsp;
In some moments of the video, the alleged niece insists that his uncle signs the practices > in order to complete and leave them, going to manipulate his hands to take a pen and try to sign. "Zio you have to sign. The gentleman must sign. I can't sign for the gentleman. The gentleman must hold the pen tight and sign here," says the woman as she moves the hands of the corpse in front of the bank employees, who insist on warning that the man is miserable and very pale.<br> Commissioner Fabio Souza, in charge of the investigation, said he had already asked the courts to order the final arrest of the accused and that he is trying to determine if he had any accomplices.

